## 5. Database Schema Design

### Schema: `ai_studio`

### Table: `ai_studio.generations`
| Column | Type | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| id | UUID PK | Generation request ID |
| customer_id | VARCHAR(255) | Medusa customer who requested |
| prompt | TEXT | User's original prompt |
| style | VARCHAR(50) | Selected style (Luxury, Cartoon, etc.) |
| occasion | VARCHAR(50) | Selected occasion (Birthday, Wedding, etc.) |
| flavor | VARCHAR(50) | Selected flavor |
| zodiac_sign | VARCHAR(20) | Optional zodiac |
| zodiac_suggestion | TEXT | Optional zodiac design suggestion |
| provider | VARCHAR(30) | replicate / openai / stability |
| provider_model | VARCHAR(100) | black-forest-labs/flux-1.1-pro |
| status | VARCHAR(20) | pending → processing → completed / failed |
| image_count | INT | Number of images generated |
| credit_cost | INT | Credits consumed |
| failed_reason | TEXT | Error message if failed |
| created_at | TIMESTAMPTZ | Request time |
| started_at | TIMESTAMPTZ | When provider call started |
| completed_at | TIMESTAMPTZ | When generation finished |
| duration_ms | INT | Total time taken |

### Table: `ai_studio.cake_designs`
| Column | Type | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| id | UUID PK | Unique design ID |
| generation_id | UUID FK | Links to parent generation |
| customer_id | VARCHAR(255) | Who generated this |
| image_url | TEXT | Permanent S3 URL |
| s3_key | TEXT | S3 object key (for management) |
| image_index | SMALLINT | Position in batch (0, 1, 2) |
| prompt | TEXT | Original prompt |
| style | VARCHAR(50) | Style used |
| occasion | VARCHAR(50) | Occasion |
| flavor | VARCHAR(50) | Flavor |
| zodiac_sign | VARCHAR(20) | Optional |
| provider | VARCHAR(30) | Which AI provider |
| provider_model | VARCHAR(100) | Which model |
| tags | TEXT[] | Auto-derived searchable tags |
| embedding | VECTOR(512) | Future: visual similarity |
| view_count | INT | Times shown in recommendations |
| save_count | INT | Times saved by users |
| order_count | INT | Times led to an order |
| is_public | BOOLEAN | Can be shown to others |
| is_featured | BOOLEAN | Admin-curated |
| status | VARCHAR(20) | active / archived / deleted / flagged |
| created_at | TIMESTAMPTZ | Creation time |
| updated_at | TIMESTAMPTZ | Last update |

### Indexes
- `generation_id` — group designs by request
- `customer_id` — user's history
- `style`, `occasion`, `flavor` — attribute search
- `tags` (GIN) — tag-based filtering
- `is_public, is_featured` (partial, WHERE status='active') — recommendations
- `created_at DESC` — chronological listing

