## 9. Generation Flow (End-to-End)

```
Frontend                          Backend API                        Services
────────                          ───────────                        ────────

User fills form                        │
User clicks Generate                   │
        │                              │
        ▼                              │
POST /store/ai-studio/generate ───────►│
  { prompt, style, occasion,           │
    flavor, zodiac }                   │
                                       ▼
                              1. Authenticate (JWT)
                              2. Rate limit check (Redis)
                              3. Credit check (customer metadata or DB)
                              4. Set generation lock (Redis)
                              5. Create generation record (status: pending)
                                       │
                                       ▼
                              6. Build prompt (prompt-builder.ts)
                              7. Call AI provider (provider-factory → replicate-provider)
                              8. Receive temporary image URLs
                                       │
                                       ▼
                              9. Upload images to S3 (s3-uploader.ts)
                              10. Extract tags (tag-extractor.ts)
                              11. Save cake_designs records
                              12. Update generation record (status: completed)
                              13. Deduct credit
                              14. Release generation lock
                                       │
                                       ▼
                              Return response ──────────────────► Frontend
                              { generationId, designs[], creditsRemaining }
```

